### Portfolio API Tests
### Base URL for local development
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@contentType = application/json

### ========================================
### CREATE PORTFOLIO - SUCCESS CASES
### ========================================

### Create portfolio with valid data
POST {{baseUrl}}/portfolios
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "cash": 10000.50
}

### Create portfolio with zero cash
POST {{baseUrl}}/portfolios
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "jane.smith@example.com",
  "cash": 0
}

### Create portfolio with large cash amount
POST {{baseUrl}}/portfolios
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "investor@example.com",
  "cash": 1000000.99
}

### ========================================
### CREATE PORTFOLIO - ERROR CASES
### ========================================

### Missing email
POST {{baseUrl}}/portfolios
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "cash": 5000
}

### Missing cash
POST {{baseUrl}}/portfolios
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "test@example.com"
}

### Negative cash amount
POST {{baseUrl}}/portfolios
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "cash": -100
}

### Invalid cash type (string instead of number)
POST {{baseUrl}}/portfolios
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "cash": "5000"
}

### Empty request body
POST {{baseUrl}}/portfolios
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{}

### ========================================
### EDGE CASES
### ========================================

### Very long email
POST {{baseUrl}}/portfolios
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "very.long.email.address.that.might.cause.issues@verylongdomainname.com",
  "cash": 1000
}

### Special characters in email
POST {{baseUrl}}/portfolios
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "test+tag@example.com",
  "cash": 1000
}

### Decimal cash with many places
POST {{baseUrl}}/portfolios
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "precision@example.com",
  "cash": 1234.56789
}

### ========================================
### INVALID REQUESTS
### ========================================

### Wrong HTTP method (GET instead of POST)
GET {{baseUrl}}/portfolios

### Wrong content type
POST {{baseUrl}}/portfolios
Content-Type: text/plain

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "cash": 1000
}

### Malformed JSON
POST {{baseUrl}}/portfolios
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "cash": 1000,
} 